{"lemma":"ظَرْفِ","slug":"ظَرْفِ","root":"ظ.ر.ف","root_slug":"ظ-ر-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/ظ-ر-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":11},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27536","n27540","n27541"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B8%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%81%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"vessel, container, receptacle"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"metal saucer"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"box, pasteboard box, purse, bag"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"egg cup"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"envelope (for a letter)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"case"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cover"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"adverb, adverbial expression denoting place or time"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"circumstance, condition"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"wit, sagacity"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gracefulness, elegance, culture"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ðˤarf/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27536","headword_ar":"ظَرُفَ","root":"Zrf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, &c.,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaraAfapN","text_ar":"ظَرَافَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZarofN","text_ar":"ظَرْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaraAfapN","text_ar":"ظَرَافَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, M, Mgh, * O, K,) but the latter is rare, (K,) allowable in poetry, (T, M,) or, as some say, is of frequent occurrence, and confirmed by analogy, (MF, TA,) said of a man, (S, O,) [or only of a young man, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zarufat","text_ar":"ظَرُفَت"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a young woman,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He possessed the quality,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"qualities, termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zarof","text_ar":"ظَرْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning as expl. below [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excellence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elegance, in mind, manners,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"address"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speech;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in person, countenance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garb, guise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"external appearance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"all of these qualities combined: he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, clever, ingenious, intelligent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acute in intellect; well-mannered, well-bred, accomplished,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"polite; beautiful in person"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"countenance; elegant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"graceful;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elegant in garb, guise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"external appearance"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (T, S, O, Msb, K.)       -A2-  See also what here follows."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","T","M","MF","TA","O"]},{"entry_id":"n27540","headword_ar":"ظَرْفٌ","root":"Zrf","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A receptacle"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T, S, M, Mgh, O, Msb, K) of anything; (Lth, T, M;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a vessel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vase;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iboriyq","text_ar":"اـِبْرِيق"},{"kind":"text","text":"is thus termed as being a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zrf","text_ar":"ظرف"},{"kind":"text","text":"for what is in it: (Lth, T, TA:) and AHn applies it to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a seed-vessel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pericarp,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a cell of a pericarp:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) [and it is also applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cover,"},{"kind":"text","text":"for a book or the like:] the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZuruwfN","text_ar":"ظُرُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, S, * M, Mgh, O, Msb, K:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aZoraAfN","text_ar":"اَظْرَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a mistake. (Mgh.) [Applying it to a vessel of silver,] Har uses it as meaning “ silver. ” (P. 614 [referring to a phrase in p. 213].) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*otu AlmataAEa biZarofihi","text_ar":"اَخَذْتُ المَتَاعَ بِظَرْفِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I took the goods with the receptacle thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) And hence, (A, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^ayotuhu biZarofihi","text_ar":"رَاَيْتُهُ بِظَرْفِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I saw him himself."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, O, K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa naqiY~u AlZ~arofi","text_ar":"هُوَ نَقِىُّ الظَّرْفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is faithful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not treacherous."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, O, K, TA.) ―         -b2-  And hence (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An adverbial noun"},{"kind":"text","text":"of place or of time,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"implying the meaning of the preposition"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fY","text_ar":"فى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and also by some applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a noun"},{"kind":"text","text":"of place or of time"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"together with that preposition;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.] what are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zarofu AlmakaAni","text_ar":"ظَرْفُ المَكَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alz~amaAni","text_ar":"الزَّمَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zuruwfu Alz~amaAni","text_ar":"ظُرُوفُ الزَّمَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmakaAni","text_ar":"المَكَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, M: *) the descriptive terms that denote the places [or times] of things are called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZuruwfN","text_ar":"ظُرُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Lth, T:) they are thus termed by Kh; and by Ks,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAl~u","text_ar":"مَحَالُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and by Fr,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SifaAtN","text_ar":"صِفَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T.) ―         -b3-  Also ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Excellence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elegance, in mind, manners,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"address"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speech;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in person, countenance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garb, guise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"external appearance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"all of these qualities combined:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] a term denoting"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a condition that combines the generality of mental and bodily and extrinsic excellences;"},{"kind":"text","text":"likened [by reason of its comprehensiveness] to the receptacle thus called: (Er-Rághib, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cleverness, ingeniousness, intelligence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acuteness in intellect;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kiyaAsapN","text_ar":"كِيَاسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kayosN","text_ar":"كَيْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*akaA='N","text_ar":"ذَكَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraAEapN","text_ar":"بَرَاعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*akaA='u qalobK","text_ar":"ذَكَا=ءُ قَلْبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [the former meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excellence in knowledge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other qualities;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accomplishment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perfection, in every excellence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in goodliness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] ('Eyn, M, O, Msb, K; *) thus accord. to most of the copies of the K [as well as the 'Eyn and M and O and Msb], but correctly"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bazaAEap","text_ar":"بَزَاعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", with the letter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zAY","text_ar":"زاى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) [if so, these two explanations ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bazaAEapN","text_ar":"بَزَاعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*akaA='u qalobK","text_ar":"ذَكَا=ءُ قَلْبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":") add nothing to others here given:] or"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1911},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skilfulness"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA) is thus termed by the people of El-Yemen: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is in the tongue,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"only;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beauty of expression,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eloquence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaAwapN","text_ar":"حَلَاوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is in the eyes, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malaAHapN","text_ar":"مَلَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is in the mouth, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAlN","text_ar":"جَمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is in the nose: (IAar, T:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beauty of garb, guise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"external appearance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beauty of face,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of garb, guise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"external appearance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is in the face"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the tongue:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ks, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goodliness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beauty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adab","text_ar":"اَدَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as having the meaning first assigned to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZarofN","text_ar":"ظَرْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this sentence, i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excellence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elegance, in mind, manners,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"address"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speech;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good breeding, good manners, politeness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"polite accomplishments"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb:) or, as an inf. n., the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being elegant, graceful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beautiful:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being intelligent, sagacious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acute in intellect:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL:) accord. to the author of the 'Eyn, (O,) it is only an attribute of young men and young women (M, O, Msb, * K) that are acute in intellect, clever, or skilful; (M, O, K;) not of elders, nor of lords, or chiefs: (M, K:) but as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kiyosN","text_ar":"كِيْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", it is common to young persons and elders: (Msb:) some of those who affect distinctness of speech by twisting the sides of the mouth say that the word is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZurofN","text_ar":"ظُرْفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm, to distinguish it from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZarofN","text_ar":"ظَرْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning “ a receptacle; ” but this is a sheer mistake. (MF, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Lth","T","S","M","Mgh","O","Msb","K","TA","A","IAar","L","Ks","KL"]},{"entry_id":"n27541","headword_ar":"ظُرْفٌ","root":"Zrf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what immediately precedes."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}